
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "demo";
}

<div class="invoice">
    <div class="invoice-company text-inverse">
        <span class="pull-right label label-primary">标准确认单</span>
        <span class="pull-right label label-warning">直签确认单</span>
        东方天呈订单确认单
    </div>
    <div class="invoice-header">
        <div class="invoice-from">
            <small>甲方</small>
            <address class="m-t-5 m-b-5">
                <strong>东方天呈文化传媒有限公司</strong><br>
                高新区交子大道177号1栋1单元15层1505-1510号<br>
                成都, 610000<br>
                电话: 028-61511999
            </address>
        </div>
        <div class="invoice-to">
            <small>乙方</small>
            <address class="m-t-5 m-b-5">
                <strong>成都网泰文化传媒有限公司  </strong><br>
                天府新区兴隆街道办事处场镇社区正街57号2幢1单元3号<br>
                成都, 610000<br>
                电话: 028-85327970
            </address>
        </div>
        <div class="invoice-date">
            <small>广告发布内容</small>
            <div class="date m-t-5">铜雀台</div>
            <div class="invoice-detail">
                成都铜雀台整形美容医院有限公司<br>
                2016-12-15 到 2017-01-15
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="invoice-content">
        <div class="table-responsive">
            <table class="table table-invoice">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>投放城市</th>
                        <th>投放单位（秒）</th>
                        <th>投放规格</th>
                        <th>数量</th>
                        <th>投放时长（小时）</th>
                        <th>单价（元）</th>
                        <th>单项总价（元）</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            一线城市<br>
                            <small>北京，上海</small>
                        </td>
                        <td>5</td>
                        <td>360次/天 * 14</td>
                        <td>380</td>
                        <td>291666.67</td>
                        <td>￥ 50.00</td>
                        <td>￥ 2,500.00</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            其他城市<br>
                            <small>成都，重庆，杭州</small>
                        </td>
                        <td>5</td>
                        <td>240次/天 * 14</td>
                        <td>380</td>
                        <td>291666.67</td>
                        <td>￥ 50.00</td>
                        <td>￥ 2,500.00</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        <div class="row">

        </div>
        <div class="invoice-price">
            <div class="invoice-price-left">
                <div class="invoice-price-row">
                    <div class="sub-price">
                        <small>总价</small>
                        $4,500.00
                    </div>
                    <div class="sub-price">
                        <i class="fa fa-minus"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="sub-price">
                        <small>其他 (刊钱全款优惠 5.4% ) <a href="javascript:openPaymentType();">选择其他支付方式</a> </small>
                        $108.00
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="invoice-price-right">
                <small>合计</small> $4508.00
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row pull-right m-t-20">
            <p class="m-r-20">
                <a href="javascript:;" class="btn btn-grey btn-sm m-r-5">&nbsp;&nbsp; 取消 &nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
                <a href="javascript:;" class="btn btn-pink btn-sm">&nbsp;&nbsp; 保存 &nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="invoice-note">
        * 本确认单作为合同款结算的依据，属于原合同不可分割的附件；若甲方为集团公司 则甲方需保证每次确认单签字盖章公司与之后付款主体保持一致.<br>
        * 本确认单一式俩份，甲乙方各执一份；与原合同具有同等法律效力。本确认单签字或盖章均生效，在本确认单上签字人即视为该方授权代表。（若签字需提供公司出具授权书）<br>
        * 发布工作完成后提供工作成果样报、样刊.附带户外广告位置附表.
    </div>
</div>

<!--Add modal begin-->
<div class="modal fade" id="modal-payment-list">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true" onclick="">×</button>
                <h4 class="modal-title">选择其他支付方式</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <h5>现金转账</h5>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="radio-inline">
                        <input type="radio" name="optionsRadios" value="option1" checked="">
                        刊前全款
                    </label>
                    <label class="radio-inline">
                        <input type="radio" name="optionsRadios" value="option2">
                        刊前50%， 刊后一个月内支付剩余50%
                    </label>
                </div>
                <h5>承兑汇票</h5>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="radio-inline">
                        <input type="radio" name="optionsRadios" value="option1" checked="">
                        银行承兑
                    </label>
                    <label class="radio-inline">
                        <input type="radio" name="optionsRadios" value="option2">
                        商业承兑
                    </label>
                </div>
                <div class="alert alert-danger m-b-0">
                    <p>选择此项时，请提前与媒介主沟通，是否承认有关承兑和承兑时间</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@section Scripts {
    <script>
        function openPaymentType() {
            $("#modal-payment-list").modal('show');
        }
    </script>
}